---
/**
 * Board Size Comparison Page
 * 
 * Interactive comparison of various development boards showing their relative sizes,
 * specifications, and capabilities. Visitors can hover (desktop) or tap (mobile)
 * on each board to see details and navigate to the full device page.
 */

